hackathon-eligibility: Teams of Baylor University Students (all majors)
hackathon-requirements: No need to submit, just present your work in person.
hackathon-rules:
Make use of built-in libraries, etc.
Come up with new ideas.  Reusing some old code is okay, but you can't reuse entire projects.
Entries will be judged against three categoies: Best Idea, Best Execution, Most Innovative.

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: Given more time, would the project become a useful or successful product?
